\mt1 FILIPAI
\c 1
\s1 POL FILIPAI KAT P∆óL∆óWUTA PAS
\p 
\v 1 Wun Pol wun. Timoti wunogwio t…®gand…®. An Kraist Jisasna nj…®vwa kwut…®ga nyanli. Filipai wal…®nja ngepmamba Godna mbaapma n…®mba kat kan pas p…®l…®wutaa kwil…®gowun. Ngwuk Kraist Jisasna nyaang…®t ngwutna maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa t…®gangwuk. Ngwulogwi l…®ka njambwi n…®mba ndinogwi wutnjangat kan pas p…®l…®wutaa ngwuk kat kwili…®gowun. Ngwuk kat Godna nj…®vwa kwuka s…®mogwi l…®ga nyangu kat ndino ndi kat p…®l…®wut…®gowun.
\v 2 N…®na nyaek God n…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraist ngwuk kat apma vat yelav…®ka yet…®ngweya maawut awagapma kwimbamb…®t walaa ngwuk kat wowun.
\s1 POL GOD KAT S∆óVU K∆óND∆ó
\p 
\v 3 T…®ga l…®ga ngwuk kat yelav…®ka tuwa nj…®mbla wuna njambwi nyan God kat gwuk kat t…®ga s…®vu k…®l…®gowun.
\v 4 Ngwuk kat t…®ga God kat wagalaweya nj…®mbla n…®ma vat solat s…®l…®gowun.
\v 5 Tamba l…®ga wan apma nyaang…®t but…®wa nj…®mbla wunogwi nala k…®ta vat nj…®vwa kwut…®ngwuk. Yiga l…®ga mbambala wunogwinala k…®ta vat at kwut…®gangwuk. Wunogwinala k…®ta vak nj…®vwa kwut…®ngwa vak kat yelav…®taa ngwuk kat n…®ma vat solat s…®l…®gowun.
\v 6 K…®ta da tamba v…®ga l…®gowun. Tak God ngwuk kat kwunapmak nj…®vwa kwut…®nd…®. Ngwuk kat kwunaka l…®ga y…®ga Kraist Jisas yaiga nj…®mblamba apma vat t…®giyangwuk. Ngwuk kat kwunat…®nda nj…®vwa ng…®l…®nd…® maa Kraist Jisas yaigand…®. V…®ga l…®gowun.
\v 7 Nj…®mbla ngwuk kat yelav…®ka luwa vat nglaatnd…®. Tamba wan apma nyaang…®t yi ya butuwa nj…®mbla wunogwinala k…®ta vat nj…®vwa kwut…®ngwuk. Mbutuwa nyaang…®t kat kaiwalaa wun kat kalabusmba taagandi. Mbambala wun kalabusmba l…®wun, wun kat ana kwagala l…®gangwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga ngwuk kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®gowun.
\v 8 Ngwuk kat wuna maawupmba yelav…®ka tuwa vat Kraist Jisas nd…®no ngwuk kat yelav…®ka l…®nda vat k…®ta vakna. Ngwuk kat woseka ana wowun. God v…®ga l…®gand…®.
\v 9 Ngwuk kat t…®ga god kat wagalaweya nj…®mbla kupma wagalal…®gowun. Nat n…®mba kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®nja maawut yiga n…®ma yimband…® walaa wal…®gowun ndi kat. Godna angwa vat v…®ga wuka t…®nja vak n…®ma yimband…® walaa ndi kat wal…®gowun. Kan vat apma vat kan vat kavle vat waa s…®ga nagul…®nja apma vat yiga n…®ma yimband…® walaa wal…®gowun ndi kat waa wupma God kat wagala l…®gowun ngwuk kat t…®ga.
\v 10 Wagala luwa vat klangweyan apma vat t…®ga kavle vat kwagalalaa apma vat m…®na t…®giyangwuk. Ng…®ni Kraist yaiga nandinya ngwuk kavle vat ana l…®giyand…® ngwulamba. Apma vat m…®na l…®giyand…® ngwulamba. nat n…®mba ngwuk kat v…®laga ndi kavle n…®mba ndi waga ana ngwuk kat waigandi.
\v 11 Jisas Kraist ngwuk kat kwiya apma vapba yet…®giyangwuk. Wan apma vak nat nyanamba ana klaigangwuk. Nat n…®mba yet…®lingwa vak v…®lagalaga Godna s…® kwutaa katsoga apma nyan m…®n waa waigandi.
\s1 POL KALABUSMBA LINDA VAT
\p 
\v 12 Wuna mbaapmamba l…®ga n…®mba mbambala k…®ta vat v…®ngwan kat wowun. Wun kat kwutaa kalabusmba taaganja vak kavle vat ana nd…®. Taagandi maa v…®laa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba wan apma nyaang…®t wutndi. Kan apma vakna.
\v 13 Wun kat kalabusma taagandi maa v…®laa nd…® Kraistna nj…®vwa kwut…®ndan kat v…®laa nd…® kat kalabusmba taagandi waa wal…®gandi. Njambwi nyan Sisana gay v…®ga la n…®mbo nat n…®mba v…®laa wupma wal…®gandi. Kan apma vakna.
\v 14 N…®na k…®ta mbaapma n…®mba kalabusmba tuwa vat v…®laa vaaka l…®nja vak kwagalalaa wan apma nyaang…®t vaat tapmannat n…®mba kat mbut…®gandi.
\p 
\v 15 Nat nimba wun kat kai walaa Krasitna apma nyaang…®t yiga mbuka pol kat kwagalalaa n…®na kwupmba yagwa ngwula waa wal…®gandi. Nat n…®mba Pol nd…® apma nyana waa Kraistna apma nyaang…®t v…®ga mbut…®gandi.
\v 16 Wuna s…® katsoga nyaang…®t mbut…®ga n…®mba wun kat woviyaguga l…®gandi. Tak God wunkat wand…® maa kavle nyaang…®k kat kai walaa wan apma nyaang…®t m…®na mbut…®gowun. Ndi wan n…®mba kwutuwa nj…®vwa kat v…®gal…®gandi. God wan nj…®vwa Pol kat kwind…® waa v…®ga l…®gandi.
\p 
\v 17 Wun kat wal…®ga n…®mba kavle maawut yelav…®ka l…®ga Kraistna apma nyaang…®t mbut…®gandi. Avla n…®na s…® katsol…®na vak Pol kalabusmba l…®ga v…®laa nd…® mbang…® val…® yil…®nd…®, t…®gand…®. Apma vatna waa yelav…®taa mbut…®gandi.
\v 18 Apma maawut yelav…®ka kavle maawut yelav…®ka mbut…®njeyan wovuna. Nd…®na mala. Kraistna apma nyaang…®t mbut…®njeyan wun wutaa solat s…®giywoun.
\s1 KAN K∆óPMAMBA KWO L∆óWEYAN JISASO T∆óGIYOWUN
\p 
\v 19 Kalabusmba t…®wun, wun kat God kat wagala l…®gangwuk kalabus kwagalalaa wogwewangat God kat wagala l…®ngwa vat v…®ga l…®gowun. Jisas Kraist kwiya waagan nd…®na apma maawut wun kat kwil…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga kalabusmba t…®ga kwagalalaa wogweweya vak v…®ga l…®gowun.
\v 20 Wunai yelav…®ka l…®ga vat k…®ngiyan. God wun kat kwiya nj…®vwa wun kwagala vak kat kai wowun. Nandinya nandinya vaat tapman kwupmat wawun. Mbambala n…®mbun kwupmat wowun kan nj…®vwa. Kan nj…®vwa kwut…®wunmala Kraist wun kat v…®laa apma nj…®vwa kwut…®ma waigand…®. Kan nj…®vwa kwuka l…®ga kiyaweyan Kraist wun kat waigand…®. Apma nj…®vwa kwutn…®m…®n waa waigand…®.
\v 21 Kiya lapman kan k…®pmamba kwo l…®weyan wovuna. K…®pmamba kwo l…®ga Kraistnonana k…®tamba yet…®giywoun. Kiyaweyan wovuna. Kiyalaa apma wenga klalaa apma kavamba yiga l…®giyowun.
\v 22 Kiya lapman kan k…®pmamba kwo l…®weyan n…®ma sakwat apma nj…®vwa kwuka t…®giyowun. Kiyaweyan apma kavat yigiyowun. Kiyaweyan apma vakna? Kiya lapman yiweyan apma vatna? Wun ana yelav…®ka v…®ga l…®gowun.
\v 23 Maawat v…®l…®l…®k yelav…®ka l…®gowun. Kan k…®pma kwagalalaa Kraistnana yiga t…®vat t…®gowun. Apma vatna.
\v 24 K…®pmamba t…®weyan ngwukkat kwunapmak njsvwa kwukiyowun. Wan apma nglei vatna.
\v 25 Kan k…®pmamba kiya lapman kwo l…®weyan apma vala. V…®ga l…®gowun. Kwo l…®ga ngwuk kat kwunapmak kan nj…®vwa kwuka l…®giyowun. Ngwuk Kraistna nyaang…®t wutaa solat s…®ga maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®ngwuk. Ngwuk kat kwunakwun, solat s…®ngwa vat n…®ma yigiyand…®.
\v 26 Ngwutnai l…®ga kava yawun maa maawupmba yelav…®kiyangwuk. N…®n Kraist Jisas kat nd…® kat t…®ga wagalan…®n, kalabus kwagalalaa wogwelaa yand…®. Kraist Jisas kat kwutaa l…®na vat tagula vatna waa yelav…®kiyangwuk.
\s1 WUNOGWINANA NJ∆óVWA AGWUK NGWULA WAA WAND∆ó POL
\p 
\v 27 K…®ta nda n…®ma nda ngwuk kat mbukiyowun. Ngwuk apma vat m…®na yiga Kraist waa nyaang…®t m…®na wuka yet…®ngwula. Ngwuk kat ng…®ni v…®vat yaweyan apma vat yet…®ngweya vak v…®giyowun. Ng…®ni ngwuk kat v…®vat ya lapman yiweyan apma vat yet…®ngweya vak waamba wukiyowun. Ngwuk k…®ta maawut yelav…®ka k…®tamba nj…®vwa kwuka wan apma nyaang…®t mbut…®ngwa vak wukiyowun.
\v 28 Ngwuk kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba kat ke vaakngwa. Vaatapman kwondumba al…® ngwula. Vaatapmankwondumba l…®ngwa vak kai wal…®ga n…®mba v…®laa waigandi. N…®n kavle yigiyan…®n waa waigandi. God ngwuk kat kwondu kwind…®, apma vat t…®giyangwuk.
\v 29 God gwuk kat nj…®vwa kwuka t…®gangwuk. Nat k…®ta nj…®vwa k…®ngiyan kwinda. Kraistna s…® mbukngwuk maa nat n…®mba gwuk kat v…®laa n…®ma vak yigiyandi. Ngwuk wan vak kat ana kai waigangwuk.
\v 30 Wuno wun kat wupma yil…®ndi. Mbambala wuno ngwutno k…®ta nj…®vwamba kwut…®gan…®n. Mbambala kwutuwa nj…®vwa tak kwutuwa nj…®va vla kwut…®gowun. Nj…®vwa kwutuwa vak tamba waamba wuka l…®gangwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga wunokwinala k…®ta vat nj…®vwa agwuk ngwula.
\c 2
\s1 NAT N∆óMBA KAT N∆óMA MAAWUT YELAV∆óKIYAN∆óN
\p 
\v 1 Kraistna mbaapma wuleilaa kwondu maawutno l…®gangwuk? O kai. Kraist n…®n kat n…®na yelav…®ka t…®nda vat apma vatna waa yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk? Ana yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Godna waagan yelav…®ka l…®ga vat k…®ta vat yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk? Kai ana yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Awat sowat woviyaguga kwunat…®gangwuk? Ana kwunat…®gangwuk. Wungi apma nda ngwulamba t…®ndeyan wuna nyaang…®t ngwuk awuk ngwula.
\p 
\v 2 Wungi apma nda ngwutnamba l…®gand…®. V…®ga logowun. Wungi apma nda ngwulamba t…®nd…®, v…®ga l…®ga solat s…®ga l…®gowun. Ngwuk k…®ta maawupmba yelav…®ka al…® ngwula. Wupma yil…®ngweyan ngwuk kat solat s…®l…®weya vat n…®man nglei yigiyand…®.
\v 3 Avla ngwutna s…® katsovat nj…®vwa ke kwukngwa. Wun apma nyan wun waa wavat nj…®vwa ke kwukngwa. Nat nyan kat yelav…®pmbangwuk nj…®vwa kwupmak kat. Nat n…®mba kat kwulat…®gowun waa ke yelav…®kngwa.
\v 4 Ngwuk avla kwunapmak kat ke yelav…®t t…®ngwa. Nat n…®mba kat kwunakngweya vak kat yelav…®k ngwula.
\v 5 Tat Kraist Jisas yelav…®tnda vak vla mbambala ngwulo wupma yelav…®k ngwula.
\v 6 Kraist Jisas tak yelav…®tnda vak k…®ngiyand…® l…®ga. Tak nd…® God t…®nda vla t…®nd…®. God ta vla tuwa vat ana kwutaa l…®giyowun waa yelav…®ka l…®nd…®.
\v 7 Nd…®na maawupmba God t…®nda vak kwagalalaa kan k…®pma ngega yand…®. Yalaa ndunyana mbang…® klalaa ndu nyan vla l…®nd…®. Nj…®vwa kwuta nyan vla l…®nd…®.
\v 8 Nd…®na yelav…®k vapmba ana yet…®nd…®. Godnana yelav…®k vapmba yet…®nd…®. Yet…®ga l…®ga God wand…® mala kiyand…®. Diwai krosmba nd…® kat kaalandi maa kiyand…®.
\v 9 Ngi kat t…®ga God kwuta nj…®vwa kat v…®laa nd…® kat nyinangwut kalilaa njambwi nyan m…®n waa wand…®. M…®na s…® nat n…®mbana s…® kat kwulat…®gand…® waa wand…®.
\v 10 Ng…®ni nyinangwupmba l…®ga n…®mba, k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba, kiya n…®mba aywaa Jisas kat vilaa ndaa kwali mamba s…®laa nd…®na s…® kwutaa katsogiyandi.
\v 11 Jisas Kraist m…®n njambwi glei nyan m…®n waa kwundimba waigandi. Walaa n…®na nyaek God m…®n Jisas kat apma vat yim…®n waa waigandi.
\s1 YA V∆óT∆óGA LAM VLA L∆óGANGWUK
\p 
\v 12 Ali n…®mba tak ngwulogwinala l…®wun, wuna nyaang…®t wuka l…®ngwuk. Mbambala tulala s…®vlamba t…®gowun. Mbambala n…®mbun wuna nyaang…®t awuk ngwula. God ngwuk kat kwutaa tamba nd…®na mbaapmamba ngwuk kat taagand…®, t…®gangwuk. Mbambala Godna nyaang…®t wuka nd…®na nj…®vwa n…®mamba kwuka t…®giyangwuk. N…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka l…®ngweyan God ngwuk kat kwunapmat t…®nda vak klal…®giyangwuk.
\v 13 God ngwuk kat apma maawut kwil…®gand…®. Kwinda maawupmba yelav…®ka nd…®na nj…®vwa m…®na kwut…®giyangwuk.
\v 14 Kan aywaa kwut…®ngwa nj…®vwa woku walea wata kwut…®ngweya. Kwo akwuk ngwula.
\p 
\v 15 Wupma kwut…®ngweyan Godna apma nyangu vla t…®giyangwuk. Kavle vat ngwulamba ana l…®giyand…®. Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba ndi kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba ndi. Ndina n…®nd…®mba l…®ga ya vit…®ga lam vla l…®giyangwuk. Apma yamb…® ndi kat v…®s…®mogwigiyangwuk.
\v 16 Ndi kat Kraistna apma nyaang…®t mbukngwuk maa di apma yamb…®mba yigiyandi. Wupma yaigweyan wun solat s…®giyowun. Kraist yaiga nandinya wun ngwuk kat vilaa yelav…®kiyowun. Ndi kat kwunapmak kwutuwa nj…®vwa kwo nj…®vwa ana nd…® kwutuwa. Ndi tamba apma vat t…®gandi.
\p 
\v 17 Tak ngwuk kat wan apma nyaang…®t mbukwun. Mbukwun mala wutaa kwutaa l…®gangwuk. Kwutaa l…®ngwa vak God v…®laa apma vatna waa wal…®gand…®. Ngwuk kat kwunatuwa nj…®vwa ana kwagala l…®gowun. Kwutaa l…®gowun. Kan nj…®vwa kwuka l…®ga kiyaweyan apma vala. Ngwuk kat kwunakwun, ngwula maawut tagula vat tndeyan wun v…®laa solat s…®giyowun. Solat s…®weya vat ngwuk kat mbupmat wowun.
\v 18 Wawa nyaang…®t wutaa ngwulo wun kat solat s…®ngweya vat wun kat ambuk ngwula.
\s1 SAMAT T∆óGA TIMOTI NGWUK KAT YAIGAND∆ó
\p 
\v 19 Njambwi nyan Jisas kai walapman yindeyan samat t…®ga wowun maa Timoti ngwuk kat yigiyand…®. Ngwuk kat v…®laa yalaa yet…®ngwa vak wun kat yaa mbukiyand…®. Wutaa solat s…®giyowun.
\v 20 Timoti yeta vla yet…®giya nat nyan ana l…®gand…®. Nd…®no wuno k…®ta maawut yelav…®ka t…®gaa. Ngwuk kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®gand…®.
\v 21 Nat n…®mba avla ndina nda kat m…®na yelav…®ka l…®gandi. Jisas Kraistna nj…®vwa kat ana yelav…®ka l…®gandi. Nd…® wupma kai.
\v 22 Timoti kat v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Apma nyana. Nd…®nagwio wunogwio k…®ta vat wan apma nyaang…®t mbuta. Nyaek nyan vla l…®gaa.
\v 23 Timoti m…®n Filipaiat ay waa yelav…®taviga t…®gowun. Wun kat yaiga vat ana viga l…®gowun. Yaigowun? Ana yaigowun.
\v 24 N…®ma nyan kat wagala l…®gowun. Ngwutnai l…®ga kava kwiyatapman yavat wagala l…®gowun.
\s1 SAMAT T∆óGA EPAFRODAITAS NGWUK KAT YAIGAND∆ó
\p 
\v 25 Epafrodaitas kat ay wowun maa ngwuk kat nd…® yigand…®. Nd…® n…®na k…®ta mbaapma nyana. Wuno nd…®no k…®tamba Godna nj…®vwa kwut…®li maa angat vat yil…®ndi. Ngwuk kat t…®ga wun kat kwunat…®gand…®.
\v 26 Nd…®na woviyaguga vat n…®ma nglei t…®gand…® ngwuk kat v…®vat. yelogwen kat t…®nda vak kat wukngwa vak wutaa nd…® ana ngalaatnd…® wand…®. Wun kat n…®ma maawut mbaak yelav…®ka l…®gandi waa wand…®.
\v 27 Mat yelogwen ana nd…®. N…®ma yelogwena. Tamba kiya m…®na l…®nd…®. God nd…® kat miwa yilaa kwunatnd…®, laatnd…®. Wuno wun kat miwa yind…®. Epafrodaitas kiyaindan wuna mbang…® ngum…®k kwukend…®.
\v 28 Nd…® laatnd…® mala kwonduo wogwuga t…®gowun ngwula lak kwivat. Nd…® kat v…®laa solat s…®giyangwuk. Solat s…®ngweya vak wutaa wuno solat s…®vat t…®gowun.
\v 29 Ngi kat t…®ga solat s…®ga ngwula ngayat kali ngwula. Nd…®na njambwi nyanngwutna njambwi nyan k…®ta nyana. Ngwuk k…®ta yakwa n…®mba vla l…®gangwuk. nd…®nai l…®ga vla t…®ga n…®mba nd…®na s…® kwutaa katsongwula.
\v 30 Nd…® Kraistna nj…®vwa kwuka l…®ga tamba kiya m…®na l…®nd…®. Ngi vak kat ana yelav…®ka l…®nd…® kiyavak kat. Apma vak wal…®nd…®. Ngwuk s…®vlamba t…®ngwuk. Wun kat ngwuk ana al…®ts…®ga kwunat…®ngwuk. Nd…® wuna ngwaymba t…®nd…®. Ngwuk kat t…®ga wun kat kwunat…®nd…®.
\c 3
\s1 POL KRAISTNA ANGWA VAK KAT KWAT∆óGAND∆ó
\p 
\v 1 N…®na k…®ta mbaapma n…®mba ng…®ni la nyaang…®t k…®ngiyan nd…® p…®l…®wukwa. N…®ma nyan ngwuk kat apma maawut kwind…® maa solat s…®ngwan kat wowun. Tak p…®l…®wukwa nyaang…®t at nat njamb…® p…®l…®wutaa kwigiyowun. N…®ma sakwat njamb…® kan nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutaa kwiweyan wovuna. Kan nyaang…®t wuka l…®ngweyan ana kavle yigiyangwuk.
\p 
\v 2 Kavle vat yiga yet…®ga n…®mba kat v…®ga t…®giyangwuk. Ndi kwap…®mba yet…®ga waala vla t…®gandi. Ndi mbang…®na vak m…®na yelav…®ka gwutna mbang…® p…®pmak wandi.
\v 3 Mbang…® nglambi ana l…®gand…® waa p…®t…®gandi. P…®tndi maa nglambi nglambi l…®gandi. Godna waagan m…®na nglambi s…®l…®mbwil…®gand…®. N…®na maawupmba la nglambi Godna waagan ngega yaa s…®l…®mbwind…®, n…®n kwo l…®gan…®n. Mbang…®na nda n…®n ana n…®ma yelav…®ka t…®gan…®n. N…®n Kraist Jisasna mbaapmamba wuleilaa t…®gan…®n.
\v 4 Kan mbang…®na nda n…®ma nda ana nd…®. Mbang…®na nda wuna nglambi s…®l…®mbwigiyandi waa k…®ta nyan yelav…®tndeyan wan ana glaatnd…®. Kavle vakna. Tamba wupma yelav…®t…®wun. Mang…®na nda kat yelav…®ka n…®ma nj…®vwa tamba kwut…®wun. Nj…®vwa kwuka nat n…®mba kat tamba kwulakwun.
\v 5 Mat nyan t…®ga wuna nandinya s…®la kuvuk t…®nd…®, wuna mbang…® p…®tndi. Wuna nyaek ny…®me Isrel n…®mba mb…®k. Wuna yelang…® Bensamin wal…®nja yelang…®. Judana angwa yelang…®. Nat yelang…® kat kwulaka t…®gand…®. Judana vak wuta kan vapmba m…®na yet…®wun. Ferisi yet…®na vak vla yet…®wun.
\v 6 Judana vak n…®mamba kwutaa l…®wun. Kwutaa l…®ga Kraistna mbaapma n…®mba kat s…®ga viya l…®wun. Judana vak ana kai waa kal…®kwun. Nat nyan yet…®wa vak v…®laa waged…®. Nd…® Pol Judana vak aywaa wuka yet…®l…®gand…® waa wagend…®.
\v 7 Tamba yetuwa vak kat yelav…®kwun. Yetuwa vak apma vatna waa yelav…®kwun. Mbambala wupma ana yelav…®kowun. Kraistna mbaapma wuleilaa mand…®p vat yelav…®k vak yelav…®kowun. Tamba yetuwa vak kwo vatna waa yet…®wun mbambala yelav…®kowun.
\v 8 Yetuwa vak m…®na wupma ana yelav…®kowun. Kan k…®pmana ka kat aywaa kwo da waa yelav…®kowun. N…®ma nda k…®ta l…®gand…®. Wuna njambwi nyan Kraist Jisasna angwa vat v…®vak wal…®gowun. Kan n…®ma vatna. Nat nda kavle vak vla l…®nd…®, kai waga yaagil…®…® Kraistna angwa vak kat kwat…®gowun mbambala.
\v 9 Nd…®nokwinana k…®tamba yet…®vat wawun. Judana vak wuka yet…®ga apma nyan wun waa ana waigowun. Apma nyanat tuwa vatna angwa kwutuwa nj…®vwa ana nd…®. Apma nyanat tuwa vatna angwa Kraist kat maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa luwa vatna.
\v 10 Kraistna angwa vat m…®na v…®vat yelav…®ka t…®gowun. Kiyand…®, God nd…® kat kwondu kwind…®, laatnd…®. Wungi kwondu klavat t…®gowun. Tak Kraist kat n…®ma vat yil…®ndi. Wuno wun kat n…®ma vat y…®njangat wowun. Wuno wun kat s…®njeyan apma vatna.
