\p 
\v 12 Kraistnana angwa vat yigumba ana v…®ga l…®gowun. Samat m…®na v…®ga l…®gowun. N…®ma ana v…®ga l…®gowun. Wungi vat v…®vat n…®ma nj…®vwa kwut…®gowun. Tak wun kat kwunapmak Jisas Kraist n…®ma nj…®vwa nd…®no kwut…®nd…®.
\v 13 K…®ta mbaapma n…®mba mbambala ana yigumba v…®ga l…®gowun. Samat samat v…®ga l…®gowun Kraistna angwa vat. Kwutuwa nj…®vwa wuno k…®ngivat kwut…®gowun. Tamba yetuwa kavle vat kai waa kwagalalaa God wun kat kwindeya da klavat mbambala n…®ma nj…®ivwa kwut…®gowun.
\v 14 Wokwi kwulak vla t…®ga nyan vla kwut…®gowun. Wokwi kwulaka kwuka yiga kwulakweyan apma wenga klaigowun. God wun kat v…®laa waigand…®. Kraist Jisasna mbaapmamba l…®ga apma vat t…®ga nyan m…®n. Wunai l…®ga kavat yaigam…®n waa waigand…® wun kat.
\v 15 God t…®ga maawupmba t…®ga n…®mba wunai kwuka nj…®vwa vla yelav…®ka kwut…®gandi. Ngwula k…®ta nyan kwutuwa njivwa kat kai wandeyan God nd…® kat mand…®p maawut kwind…®, yelav…®kiyand…® yigumba.
\v 16 Godnanamba klana vat ana kwagala kiyan…®n. Kwagala lapman yineyan apma vat yet…®giyan…®n.
