\c 4
\s1 KWUKA KALIL∆óNJA NJ∆óVWA
\p 
\v 1 Wuna mbaapma n…®mba ngwuk kat n…®ma vat yelav…®ka t…®gowun. Ngwuk kat v…®vat yelav…®ka l…®gbowun. Ngwuk kat yelav…®ka solat s…®ga t…®gowun. Ngwuk apma vat yet…®ga ngwuk. Wovuna. Njambwi nyana mbaapma wuleilaa apma vak yet…®gnweya vak mbuka t…®gowun.
