\v 2 Tak ngwula ngepmana taagwa v…®l…®l…®kmba mbuka t…®gowun. Mb…®tna s…® Yuodias Sintiki. Walea l…®mba vat kwagalalaa k…®tamba kanaguga yet…®mb…®la. Mb…®t taagwa k…®ta mbaapmba nda mb…®t. Mb…®la njambwi nyan k…®ta nyana.
\v 3 Tak wunagwinala nj…®vwa kwutqa nyan m…®n. M…®n mb…®k kat awamba m…®n. Mb…®k walea l…®mba vak kat m…®n mb…®k kat kwunapm…®la. Tak wunogwinana yiga wan apma nyaang…®t yiga mbut…®mb…®k. Nat nyan Klemino nat n…®mbo yiga wunogwinana ndino yiga mbut…®ndi. God nd…®na s…® lavu nyigamba tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®. Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®giyaa n…®mba aywaa ndino ndi kat p…®l…®wutnd…®.
