\v 6 N…®ma vat ke yelav…®kngwa. God kat m…®na wagala ngwula. N…®n kat apma vat yil…®gam…®n waa wagala ngwula.
\v 7 Wupma wagalangweyan n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka yet…®ngwa vak ng…®l…®giyand…®. Ng…®l…®nd…®, apma maawut yelav…®ka n…®n Kraist Jisasna n…®mba n…®n waa yelav…®kiyangwuk. Ng…®ni apma maawut yelav…®kngweya vat ana ng…®l…®giyand…®.
