\v 9 Wunamba wukngwa nyaang…®t k…®ngi nyaang…®t m…®na yelav…®ka yet…® ngwula. kwutuwun, v…®ngwa vak wungi vak m…®na yelav…®ka yet…® ngwula. Wupma yelav…®ka yet…®ngweyan God ngwuk kat apma maawut kwilaa ngwulogwinana t…®giyand…®.
