\v 10 Wun kat kwingwa wenga tamba klawun. Klalaa yelav…®kowun. Ndi wun kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®gandi waa yelav…®kowun. Njambwi nyan wun kat kwunatnd…® waa yelav…®ka solat s…®ga t…®gowun. Tak wun kat njamb…® njamb…® ana kwil…®ngwuk. Ava yamb…® kai. Njamb…® njamb…® wun kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®ngwa vak v…®ga t…®gowun.
\v 11 Ngwutnamba wenga klavak wagalavak kat kai wowun. Wenga vak kat ana n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®gowun. Kwuta luwa nda ngiyambak kwutaa luwa. Nat nda klavat kat kai wowun.
\v 12 Wenga nda lapman t…®weyan ana yelav…®t…®gowun. Nd…®na mala. Wenga nda n…®ma sakwat t…®weyanana yelav…®t…®gowun. Nd…®na mala. Wuna maawat kupma l…®gand…®. Ngepma ngepmamba t…®weyan kava kavamba l…®weyan ana yelav…®kowun. Wund…® kat t…®weyan wun yaak k…®l…®wun mala tatndeyan nd…®na mala. Kwanda kwanda lapman kwanda kwanda n…®ma sakwat t…®ndeyan nd…®na mala.
