\v 15 Tak wan apma nyaang…®t ngambuvak laakwa nandinya Masedonia kwagalalaa nyaang…®t mbupmat yiwun. Yiwun maa Godna mbaapmamba la nat n…®mba wun kat wenga ana kwil…®ndi. Filipaimba l…®ga n…®mba ngwula kapma apma wenga wun kat kwil…®ngwuk. N…®ma sakwat njamb…® wun kat kwil…®ngwuk, klawun.
\v 16 Tesalonaikamba kwo l…®wun, n…®ma sakwat njamb…® wenga kwil…®ngwuk, klawun.
